				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The different states for a Gondian in the foundry. In this dialogue Frell can be - terrified and working on a watcher under the watchful gaze of an overseers, post fight with said overseers, post the iron throne exploding (doesn't know if his mother is safe or not), and alone now that toobin (his leader) has been killed and he doesn't know what to do."
				}
